{"tid":264350,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"所有叫ASHLEY既都係臭閪!!!!! 一人N個又肥又樣衰既仆街上司/同事","createTime":"2017-05-30T17:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T05:27:46.000Z","uid":119998,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c35f4883d58efdf511fe27fddef9966b7ad98e3f","tid":264350,"uid":119998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:38:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有叫ASHLEY既都係臭閪</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有叫ASHLEY既都係臭閪</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有叫ASHLEY既都係臭閪</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢條臭肥閪係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">SUNGLAXX HUT</span>既RM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢肥得黎個格又衰又港女態度又差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵個幾雞野就係到大枝野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<ins>節錄部分罪狀 集合左部分同事既經歷 唔講太多驚自爆</ins><br />\n<br />\n罪狀1 更表問題<br />\n- 好遲都唔編更表 今日俾聽日/後日既更<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n- HOLD起左PT D時間,唔俾更又唔通知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n- FT同事REQ假, 事前通知佢OK左先CONFIRM某星期六日要放孖, 點知之後就係其他日子編D西更俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n罪狀2 用言語欺凌同事<br />\n- 我返工唔撚係受你氣架屌你老母臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n- 係另一間分店企緊既時候, 打去另一間分店鬧同事, 亦都有當面鬧 (有粗口)<br />\n其實大家都係成年人好聲好氣講 大家都夾得開心D 態度同言語都好閪<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">罪狀3 肥 <br />\n令我呢世對肥婆都有好深好大既陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家係機場/東涌OUTLET/葵興新OUTLET/<strong>朗豪坊/TST SOGO分店</strong>就可以見識到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得斑返枝美極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n零售業既巴絲打有冇對付無理同事既策略?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n快D一齊屌鳩佢地!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後奉勸大家,千祈唔好做呢間公司,無論FT/PT<br />\n依家轉左蝗蟲管真係狗也不屌,無論FT/PT<br />\n完"},{"pid":"6288c299aa81d9bab4bf56131758edd20dabe6f4","tid":264350,"uid":64558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:39:55.000Z","msg":"留名跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5798b8312c9bb055c7876b32f887837505b9e1e","tid":264350,"uid":23122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e597010249675460af5c36f644d2f7746b4daf","tid":264350,"uid":10743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:40:57.000Z","msg":"真。。。"},{"pid":"0a19aa336cf9e17a8792356bff29f635e99d2c9a","tid":264350,"uid":64558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:43:27.000Z","msg":"睇完唔敢返btw<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17484388bef9de149cc356ffe6262e5c3f02f6b5","tid":264350,"uid":42379,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:44:17.000Z","msg":"Ashley呢個名真心好臭閪港女格"},{"pid":"f7fc347f1e64829437e41713e4ac1878c0165148","tid":264350,"uid":119998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:45:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n派咩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1144837bd8ebc5be845bb9e5404357ee6711aa4f","tid":264350,"uid":119998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:47:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真。。。</blockquote><br />\n真‧弱雞絲打被恰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7270ae05